{"tid":2103384,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"德國邀中國大使會面關注香港局勢","createTime":"2020-07-11T07:06:05.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-11T07:11:02.000Z","uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"434d442c6aa7c05620a7bed162486639cf479a39","tid":2103384,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T07:06:05.000Z","msg":"德國外交部官員與駐當地中國大使會面，表達對港區國安法的關注。<br />\n<br />\n德國外交部表示，邀請了中國駐德國大使吳懇當地周五與國務秘書貝格爾會面。指德國政府與歐盟多次強調，國安法嚴重削弱香港自治、損害司法獨立和法治。中國駐德國大使館則指，吳懇闡明中方立場，批評一些勢力利用香港嚴重威脅中國國家安全，制定港區國安法是要更好落實「一國兩制」原則。強調香港事務純屬中國內政，中方反對任何形式的外部干涉。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/30038\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F30038&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyJktsUQkmpJZziL8xq2DbDY%3D&h=bd93ead2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fcablenews.i-cable.com%2Fci%2Fvideopage%2Fnews%2F30038&h=5cb3ef8f\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://cablenews.i-cable.com/ci/videopage/news/30038</a>"},{"pid":"1209c7cf1988263e010d3821923fe25a9faf980f","tid":2103384,"uid":155095,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T07:11:02.000Z","msg":"做完樣繼續奶共 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}